longBusinessSummary: Iron Road Limited explores and evaluates iron ore properties in Australia. Its 100% owned principal project is the Central Eyre iron project located on the Eyre Peninsula of South Australia. The company also engages in the development of the Cape Hardy Stage I port. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Adelaide, Australia. Iron Road Limited operates as a subsidiary of Sentient Executive GP IV, Limited.
